member_experience_collection.title: Director of Product Planning
member_experience_collection.description:
As a founding employee of this venture-backed startup in the Dallas area, Kent oversaw software development for layered products, and later for the ConvexOS operating system. member_patents_collection.title: Dynamic Question Template System and Architecture
member_patents_collection.description: Methods for generating questions useful for student evaluation. Allows an author to compose a dynamic question template (DQT). The DQT may have a question, question variables, a correct answer, and question constraints. The system may compile the DQT and generate and store a DQT object in an object library. The system can then pre-generate or dynamically generate in real time a plurality of unique question variants using the DQT object and without further input from the user.
